Package edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model

Class Counter

java.lang.Object
edu.umn.cs.csci3081w.project.model.Counter
public class Counter extends Object
Class for managing and incrementing unique identifiers for various entities in the simulation. The Counter class provides counters for routes, stops, buses, trains, and lines, ensuring that each entity receives a unique ID.
